body:
**Description**

Using DrawText method throw a System.MissingMethodException on visual studio 2017 when SkiaSharp.Views.Forms nuget version is over 1.60.3.


**Code**

```
public partial class MainPage : ContentPage
    {
        public MainPage()
        {
            InitializeComponent();
        }

        private void Handle_PaintSurface(object sender, SKPaintSurfaceEventArgs e)
        {
            var canvas = e.Surface.Canvas;
            using (var paint = new SKPaint())
            {
                paint.Color = Color.Black.ToSKColor();
                paint.TextSize = 30;

                canvas.DrawText("I am text", 15, 15, paint);
            }
        }
    }
```

**Expected Behavior**

Text get drawn.

**Actual Behavior**

App crash with MissingMethodExeption (screenshot below)

**Basic Information**

- Version with issue:  above 1.68.0 to 1.68.2.1
- Last known good version:  1.60.3
- IDE:  vs 2017 (correct behavior on vs 2019)
- Platform Target Frameworks:  Net Standard 2.0
  - Android: 9.0 Api 28, aslo tryed on 8.1 

- Target Devices:   various devices running over Android Oreo 8.1


